        <mxCell id="Eahc_mp1XSUesRuRunMF-8" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;- Scalabilty: System must be able to handle ~1M&amp;nbsp; (DAU).Also should be able to upload ~1M uploads and at the same time 100M+ views.&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;-Low latency: video start delay &amp;lt; 500 mili- seconds true iin low bandwidth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;-High availabilty : 99.99% uptime&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;-Consistency: Eventual consistency for likes &amp;amp; comments , High consistency for payments&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;-Efficient storage as videos consume huge storage&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;-Adaptive streaming&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
